Bulls President &amp; COO Michael Reinsdorf made the following statement in a team press release:
<blockquote>The Windy City Bulls will build on the great traditions of the Chicago Bulls and bring the enjoyment and love of the game of basketball to fans in the Northwest Suburbs. Windy City Bulls emerged as a fan favorite during our ‘Name the Team’ campaign earlier this season, and we thank the thousands of fans who helped us select a name that creates a strong connection to the region, reflects our civic pride, and extends the reach of the Bulls brand.</blockquote>
The team will play its home games at the Sears Center Arena in Hoffman Estates. They will start playing next season, with a schedule that will include 24 home games.

For updates on team news and events:
<blockquote>Visit the team website: <a href="http://www.bulls.com/dleague">www.bulls.com/dleague</a>

Follow the team on Twitter <a href="http://www.twitter.com/windycitybulls">@windycitybulls</a>

Follow the team on Instagram <a href="http://www.instagram.com/windycitybulls">@windycitybulls</a></blockquote>
If you are interested in season tickets, go to <a href="http://www.bulls.com/dleague">www.bulls.com/dleague</a> or call (847) 396-7070. Fans wanting season ticket priority will need to place a non-refundable deposit of $50.

Also according to the press release:
<blockquote>To celebrate the Windy City Bulls’ arrival in Hoffman Estates, Ill., the team will host a Fan Fest at Sears Centre Arena on Sunday, March 13<a href="http://airmail.calendar/2016-03-13%2012:00:00%20CDT">.</a> Local residents are encouraged to attend the event and enjoy activities for all ages, including face painting, a mechanical bull ride, pictures with the Bulls’ six NBA Championship trophies, a meet and greet with Bulls ambassadors and entertainers, and a variety of basketball games, among others. Parking and admission are free. Pre-registration is preferred at <a href="http://www.bulls.com/dleague">www.bulls.com/dleague</a>. By pre-registering for the event, fans will have the opportunity to win exclusive autographed merchandise.</blockquote>
<a href="http://www.chicagonow.com/bullsville/files/2016/02/Windy-City-Bulls-secondary-logo.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2330" alt="Windy City Bulls secondary logo" src="http://www.chicagonow.com/bullsville/files/2016/02/Windy-City-Bulls-secondary-logo.jpg" width="265" height="309" /></a>

&nbsp;

